## Client & organisation work

<sub>Systems I built for real clients — a Delaware startup, an independent Māori-led AI research commission, New Zealand's leading women-in-STEM charity, a women's-health-tech community in China, and an Auckland food festival — all still running today. I'm GAVIGO's Founding Principal Engineer, She Sharp's Senior Full Stack Engineer & Website Team Lead, and FemTech Weekend's CTO.</sub>

